{"tid":1066362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨：我哋話你知OK，就得㗎啦","createTime":"2019-03-18T00:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T06:20:57.000Z","uid":13663,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40eaf4e571f35dc9c18eef19195d02e3a7e3890b","tid":1066362,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】今年4月起試運行的高鐵香港段接連出現事故，日前被揭高鐵車輪磨損，但港鐵未有披露具體數據。港鐵主席馬時亨周六（26日）早上回應稱，試運就是要找出問題，強調港鐵已表明事故不影響安全，「我哋話你聽OK就得㗎喇」，認為社會應相信港鐵管理層，否則「管理層不用睡覺了」。前九鐵公司主席、現立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰則稱，不認為港鐵對事故有所隱瞞，但他的作風不同，「我做九鐵主席時好詳盡解釋，就為了釋除公眾疑慮」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b24d40e28224d19bd2cdb7e2f597832de9947cb","tid":1066362,"uid":124491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:48:34.000Z","msg":"馬時享：識閪work 唔work咩你地 又唔係工程師 繼續返工啦港豬 記住拍卡呀"},{"pid":"b99318ee0cbc9774692715338c8adbb5394bc5ea","tid":1066362,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7a0407cf424227bfb3abdf3ff6c9fa52216466","tid":1066362,"uid":162504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"馬時亨講完呢句<br />\n地鐵真係衰10年"},{"pid":"93ad48221657c4d3e594524decdda8f1c7e8c5f3","tid":1066362,"uid":110838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:13:26.000Z","msg":"識個閪咩你班港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識你地就係工程師啦<br />\n做啦傻西瓜"},{"pid":"1aa99b2db10b743adefcc9c038d26fb9a828fafd","tid":1066362,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7a0407cf424227bfb3abdf3ff6c9fa52216466","tid":1066362,"uid":162504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"馬時亨講完呢句<br />\n地鐵真係衰10年"},"citedBy":0,"re